islike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T16:06:44.000Z","msg":"一定要最後個24個鐘先開始溫"},{"pid":"761f26b466043125ae73fc91499486a6426c90e4","tid":655582,"uid":172536,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T16:12:18.000Z","msg":"每溫一個lecture食一排朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13a0dde6f0dddd29815e2c79d307ac3e3af0146","tid":655582,"uid":13343,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T16:15:09.000Z","msg":"中四前未試過唔合格<br />\n但有一科第三四次test 開始keep住唔合格<br />\n成日畀人罰留堂重測<br />\n<br />\n去到聖誕假發覺唔對路<br />\n咁落去分分鐘畀人迫drop科<br />\n<br />\n嗰科上學期得6課<br />\n成本textbook得100頁唔夠<br />\n成個假期每日用十個鐘頭時間溫一課<br />\n由頭到尾自己完整學一次<br />\n每一句每一段都迫自己要完全明晒先叫溫完<br />\n再自制精讀notes<br />\n嗰幾日除咗食飯痾屎痾尿瞓覺就係溫書<br />\n<br />\n放完假返到去<br />\n突然之間話考試前嚟次突擊測驗<br />\n幫大家溫書<br />\n考完出嚟全級最高分<br />\n之後一直去到會考前測驗考試都keep住拎85%以上<br />\n<br />\n最後會考paper1 用一半時間做一半時間對卷<br />\nPaper 2 mc 用咗廿分鐘就做晒<br />\n<br />\n過咗幾年對返考評局答案<br />\nPaper 2 100%啱晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1599e51f825594a6957c3867f21269f8b2bdc2","tid":655582,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T16:19:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbe7f2b02c15172d00707660aea2d0d953788f17","tid":655582,"uid":137740,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T17:39:37.000Z","msg":"嗰陣dse ict覺得唔對路<br />\n自問背嘢唔差<br />\n個半月一字不漏背咗成本last minute (&gt;200版A6)<br />\n諗起都覺得痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n中同們勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c3297b40d23d430ea0a4f79082327b9e4ca251","tid":655582,"uid":79171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T17:45:27.000Z","msg":"從來都無呢d技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=